---
title: Spiced Chicken on Baked Thai Style Rice with Peas, Sweet Chilli Drizzle and Peanuts
description: It only takes 10 minutes to prep this Spiced Chicken on Baked Thai Style Rice, then everything goes straight into the oven for an easy dinner that gives you time back!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R45_W41_UK_R25304-4_MAIN_low_2-d77bb774.jpg
